&lt;li&gt;Measure and evaluate KOL activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the annual brand planning process and contribute to the development of the Thought Leader annual strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate relationships, and provide direction to key agency partners and vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the broader LOQTORZI commerical team and support initiatives as appropriate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
