&lt;li&gt;Assure that Coherus GCP, GCLP, and GVP systems and records are compliant with global regulatory requirements. Partner at a senior level with Head of Quality to ensure globally aligned, timely, and regulatory‑compliant audit and inspection responses, while driving clear accountability and ownership among fuctional Heads of departments (Clin Ops and PV).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must work hands on within the Coherus Quality Management System infrastructure and systems and adapt and be responsible for developing processes and producre under the Coherus Quality Manual.&lt;/li&gt;
